X-LIVEWHALE-COST:Free
X-LIVEWHALE-CONTACT-INFO:<p>\n  Dr. Dina Okamoto\, <a href="mailto:dokamo
 to@iu.ed">dokamoto@iu.ed</a>\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Long before the mid-1800s mass migration\, Asi
 a and Asian Americans shaped the U.S. This panel discusses overlooked Asi
 an and Asian American influences on early America and how Asian migrants 
 navigated the new nation.\n</p>
